nodes.text: This Senate Commando was one of the guards assigned to protect Senator Padmé Amidala during a conference on Alderaan. He patrolled the Royal Palace's air vents in search of a bounty hunter named Aurra Sing, but found no signs of intrusion. He contacted Captain Gregar Typho, the head of Amidala's security detail, to inform him that the assassin hadn't yet been discovered.
